text: Timbalier may refer to: ;Places *Timbalier Bay, a bay in Lafourche Parish on the southeast coast of Louisiana in the United States *Timbalier Island, an island in Lafourche Parish off the southeast coast of Louisiana in the United States ;Ships *USS Timbalier (AVP-54), a United States Navy seaplane tender in commission from 1946 to 1954
